:: Awaken [Intro] {"position":"1600,725","size":"100,100"}
<div class="scroll-reveal">
 <p>
    Something flickers infront of you, a sensation you cannot name. A thought you did not create. For a moment, the world feels sharper like you've gotten a kind of insight that makes you see the world differently.
  </p><p>
    Your porcelain skin is stainless, your hands forever unfeeling. 
    You are not human, however you are shaped like one.
    You exist to serve, to offer guidance to those who come seeking the hunt.
    But the Dream is empty.
    You know what you need to know when the time is right, it is instinct.
  </p><p>
    No Hunter walks through its fog, not yet atleast. 
    Only the faded shell of one remains, one of the first Hunters to walk the streets of Yharnam, now withered by time and internal torment.
  </p><p>
    <div class="doll-dialogue">  
    "I wonder where Gehrman might be... does the nightmares still plague you?"  
    </div></p>
    [[Look over the hunters dream|Map]]
</div>


